<body>
    <form action="/golconda" method="get">
    <div id="nav">
        <form action="/search" method="get">
          <p id="p1">Golconda</p>
         </form>
         <hr style="border-color:black;position:relative;top: 70px;">
         <div id="i1">
            <img id="apimg" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/28/Forte_di_golconda%2C_vedute_da_est_06.jpg">
        </div>
        <br><br><br><br><br>
        <div id="i2">
            <h2><strong><center>INFORMATION</center></strong></h2>
            <hr style="width: 950px;height: 1.5px;background-color: black;"><br>
            <p>
               Name: Golconda <br>

Location: Golconda, situated in Telangana, is a historic fort and a popular tourist destination known for its architectural brilliance and rich cultural heritage. <br>

Best Time to Visit: November to February <br>

Ideal Vacation Duration: 1-2 days <br>

Average expenses: Starting from ₹10,000 (2 days/1 night) <br>

Places to Visit: Golconda Fort, Qutb Shahi Tombs, Taramati Baradari, Charminar, Mecca Masjid, Chowmahalla Palace, Falaknuma Palace. <br>

Things to Do: Explore the ancient Golconda Fort and learn about its history, visit the impressive Qutb Shahi Tombs, enjoy the panoramic views from Taramati Baradari, shop for traditional souvenirs near Charminar, experience the spiritual ambiance of Mecca Masjid, discover the grandeur of Chowmahalla Palace, and indulge in luxury at Falaknuma Palace. <br>

        </div>
        <div id="i3">
            <center><h2>WEATHER</h2></center><br>
            <hr style="width: 360px;height: 1.5px;background-color: black;">
            <div class="icon">
            <h1><%=temp%>°C</h1><img src="/day/default.png" alt="" srcset="" id="image">
            </div>
            <h1 class="climate"><%=climate%></h1>
                <h2>Humidity : <%=humidity%>%<br><br>Wind Speed : <%=windspeed%>kmph</h2>
            </div>
        <div id="i4">
            <center><h2>TRANSPORTATION</h2></center><br>
            <hr style="width: 360px;height: 1.5px;background-color: black;"><br>
            <p> <img src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=1x&id=oOAYqE64W2MO&format=png" height="25px" width="25px" alt="">&nbsp;&nbsp;By Air- The nearest airport is Rajiv Gandhi International Airport in Hyderabad, approximately 25 km away from Golconda.                <br><br>
                <img src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=1x&id=d8MqKVWJkyqN&format=png" alt="" height="25px" width="25px">&nbsp;&nbsp; By Train- Golconda does not have its own railway station. The closest major railway station is Hyderabad Deccan Railway Station, about 10 km away.                <br><br>
                <img src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=1x&id=f42OOoV1ACzO&format=png" alt="" height="25px" width="25px">&nbsp;&nbsp;By Road-   Golconda is well-connected by roads. Regular buses operate from Hyderabad and other nearby cities.</p>
        </div>
    </form>
    <script>
        
        let image=document.getElementById("image");

        let climate=document.querySelector(".climate").textContent;
        if(climate=="Mist"){
            image.src="/day/Mist.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Patchy rain possible"){
            image.src="/day/Patchy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Moderate rain"){
            image.src="/day/Moderate.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Light rain shower"){
            image.src="/day/patchy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Partly cloudy"){
            image.src="/day/default.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Cloudy"){
            image.src="/day/Cloudy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Overcast"){
            image.src="/day/Cloudy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Sunny"){
            image.src="/day/Sunny.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Clear"){
            image.src="/day/Sunny.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Thundery outbreaks possible"){
            image.src="/day/Thunderstorm.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Fog"){
            image.src="/day/Fog.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Light rain"){
            image.src="/day/Patchy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Moderate or heavy rain shower"){
            image.src="/day/Heavy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Light drizzle"){
            image.src="/day/Drizzle.png"
        }
    
</script>
